      • PLACE

        static final Key<java.lang.String> PLACE
        Key is used to store 'local' diff settings (ex: highlighting options) independently. Ex: to allow having different defaults in diff previews in "Commit Dialog" and "VCS Log".
        See Also:
        DiffPlaces

      • THREESIDE_DIFF_WITH_RESULT

        static final Key<java.lang.Boolean> THREESIDE_DIFF_WITH_RESULT
        Invert colors in three side conflict viewer. Default: "AB - B - AB" is colored as "Addition" (Left <- Base -> Right) With key: "AB - B - AB" is colored as "Deletion" (Left -> Merged <- Right)
